266
00:09:46.930 --> 00:09:49.060
Come on. let's go.

267
00:09:49.060 --> 00:09:51.890
Come on. come on. come
on. come on. come on.

268
00:09:51.900 --> 00:09:53.350
We're here at the McDouglas duck farm

269
00:09:53.360 --> 00:09:54.520
