271
00:09:56.230 --> 00:09:58.530
If the law won't shut 'em down. we will.

272
00:09:58.530 --> 00:09:59.870
If you want to support our mission.

273
00:09:59.870 --> 00:10:01.320
please. go to our website.

274
00:10:01.320 --> 00:10:03.090
Get mad!

275
00:10:03.100 --> 00:10:04.720
(BOY) We're right here.
We're here for you guys.

276
00:10:04.720 --> 00:10:05.700
We're coming.

277
00:10:05.700 --> 00:10:08.490
