287
00:10:27.120 --> 00:10:30.050
Exercising our First
Amendment right to protest.

288
00:10:30.050 --> 00:10:31.220
Like hell.

289
00:10:31.220 --> 00:10:32.670
You're trespassing!

290
00:10:32.670 --> 00:10:35.000
We're making sure no more
innocent ducks die today.

291
00:10:35.010 --> 00:10:37.130
Oh. don't do that!

292
00:10:37.130 --> 00:10:39.980
- Don't do that!
- Rage against the cage.

293
00:10:39.980 --> 00:10:43.250
(ALL) Rage against the cage!
Rage against the cage!

294
00:10:43.260 --> 00:10:45.570
- Rage against the cage!
- Hey. hey. hey!

295
00:10:45.570 --> 00:10:47.270
(ALL) Rage against the cage!

296
00:10:47.270 --> 00:10:50.740
Oh. no. no. no! Now that's just vandalism.
(CHANTING  CONTINUES)

297
00:10:50.740 --> 00:10:52.690
