298
00:10:52.690 --> 00:10:55.170
- (GIRL) Oh. my God!
- Oh. crap.

299
00:10:55.170 --> 00:10:57.690
(GIRL) Oh. my God!
Turn it off! Turn it off!

300
00:10:57.700 --> 00:10:59.340
Turn it off! (SCREAMING)

301
00:10:59.340 --> 00:11:01.660
(SHOUTING)

302
00:11:01.660 --> 00:11:03.680
Turn it off! Turn it off! Turn it off!

303
00:11:03.680 --> 00:11:05.680
(METALLIC SCREECHING)

304
00:11:07.680 --> 00:11:09.970
