310
00:11:21.000 --> 00:11:24.030
(MAN) I do that. I got 1.400
duck carcasses starting to rot.

311
00:11:24.030 --> 00:11:25.550
Toby. where is the key to your lock?

312
00:11:25.560 --> 00:11:27.440
- I can't find it.
- I swallowed it.

313
00:11:27.440 --> 00:11:28.760
You swallowed it?

314
00:11:28.760 --> 00:11:31.060
We didn't say anything
about swallowing the keys!

315
00:11:31.060 --> 00:11:32.850
Oh. you withheld information from your team.

316
00:11:32.860 --> 00:11:34.900
How's that working out for you?

317
00:11:34.900 --> 00:11:37.230
