<i>A rager of a party.</i>

1033
00:42:08.400 --> 00:42:11.670
<i>All things that are out of control.</i>

1034
00:42:11.670 --> 00:42:15.510
<i>And maybe that's where
our rage comes from.</i>

1035
00:42:15.510 --> 00:42:19.240
<i>A feeling that our world. our lives</i>

1036
00:42:19.240 --> 00:42:20.860
<i>are out of control.</i>

1037
00:42:20.860 --> 00:42:23.230
<i>- (REYNOLDS) I said don't move!
- (MICHAEL) Okay. okay!</i>

1038
00:42:23.230 --> 00:42:26.870
<i>(EDDIE) When we feel helpless...</i>
♪ I'm still standing 'cause I won't forget ♪

1039
00:42:26.870 --> 00:42:29.250
<i>powerless...</i>
♪ White flag. never going up ♪

1040
00:42:29.250 --> 00:42:31.650
<i>weak...</i>
♪ Never going up ♪

1041
00:42:31.650 --> 00:42:33.650
♪ No. no ♪

1042
00:42:33.650 --> 00:42:35.770
♪  White flag. never going up ♪

1043
00:42:35.770 --> 00:42:37.690
(PANTING) Hey. where's Eddie?
♪ Never going up ♪

1044
00:42:37.990 --> 00:42:39.670
<i>(LENA) He said he had other plans.</i>
♪ No. no ♪

1045
00:42:39.670 --> 00:42:43.190
(CHEERING)
♪ Smoke. fire. it's all going up ♪

1046
