<i>♪ Ohh ♪</i>

1049
00:42:54.560 --> 00:42:57.560
(GRUNTS)
♪ Won't wave my white flag. no ♪

1050
00:42:57.560 --> 00:43:01.620
<i>♪ This time I won't let go ♪</i>

1051
00:43:01.620 --> 00:43:04.030
<i>(EDDIE) The rage starts to build.</i>

1052
00:43:04.030 --> 00:43:06.050
<i>and it needs an outlet.</i>

1053
00:43:06.050 --> 00:43:09.560
<i>So what happens when we let it take over?</i>

1054
00:43:09.560 --> 00:43:12.660
<i>Do we regain control
by unleashing our fury?</i>

1055
00:43:14.780 --> 00:43:18.070
